properties.isPayment:
select id, 
    created_at,
    charge_date,
    amount,
    description,
    currency,
    status,
    amount_refunded,
    reference,
    coalesce(transaction_fee, 0) + coalesce(app_fee, 0) as transaction_fee,
    payout_date,
    0,
    funds_settlement,
    links_mandate,
    links_creditor,
    links_customer,
    links_payout,
    links_subscription,
    customers_id,
    customers_created_at,
    customers_email,
    customers_given_name,
    customers_family_name,
    customers_company_name,
    customers_address_line1,
    customers_address_line2,
    customers_address_line3,
    customers_city,
    customers_region,
    customers_postal_code,
    customers_country_code,
    customers_language ,
    customers_swedish_identity_number,
    customers_active_mandates,
    transaction_fee_tax
    from FlowFile where lower(customers_active_mandates) like '%false%'
properties.isSubscription:

    description,
    currency,
    status,
    amount_refunded,
    reference,
    coalesce(transaction_fee, 0) + coalesce(app_fee, 0) as transaction_fee,
    payout_date,
    0,
    funds_settlement,
    links_mandate,
    links_creditor,
    links_customer,
    links_payout,
    links_subscription,
    customers_id,
    customers_created_at,
    customers_email,
    customers_given_name,
    customers_family_name,
    customers_company_name,
    customers_address_line1,
    customers_address_line2,
    customers_address_line3,
    customers_city,
    customers_region,
    customers_postal_code,
    customers_country_code,
    customers_language ,
    customers_swedish_identity_number,
    customers_active_mandates,

    from FlowFile where lower(customers_active_mandates) like '%true%'
